- ❌ Use old v10 patterns (HTML table elements, `name` props on Tabs)
- ❌ Reference external design system documentation
- ❌ Create custom implementations of Canvas Kit components
- ❌ Add breadcrumbs or hierarchy path strips (hard workspace rule)
- ❌ Use yellow Banner for mock data disclaimers (use neutral BodyText at bottom)
- ❌ Override Canvas Kit styling unnecessarily

